1304 /// Helper routine of SimplifyDemandedUseBits. It tries to simplify
1305 /// "E1 = (X lsr C1) << C2", where the C1 and C2 are constant, into
1306 /// "E2 = X << (C2 - C1)" or "E2 = X >> (C1 - C2)", depending on the sign
1307 /// of "C2-C1".
